ance Criteria**:\n42: - `TargetPort` struct compiles without errors\n43: - `Port` field has `+kubebuilder:validation:Minimum=1` and `+kubebuilder:validation:Maximum=65535` markers\n44: - `Protocol` field has `+kubebuilder:validation:Enum=HTTP;HTTPS` marker\n45: - JSON tags are correctly formatted\n46: \n47: ---\n48: \n49: ### [ ] TASK-003: Define PodTemplateSpec helper type\n50: **Description**: Create `PodTemplateSpec` struct with metadata and spec fields.\n51: \n52: **Implementation File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n53: \n54: **Requirements**:\n55: - `Metadata metav1.ObjectMeta` - optional field\n56: - `Spec PodSpec` - optional field\n57: - Reuses Kubernetes core v1 types\n58: \n59: **Verification**:\n60: ```bash\n61: go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/ -run TestPodTemplateSpec\n62: ```\n63: \n64: **Acceptance Criteria**:\n65: - `PodTemplateSpec` struct compiles without errors\n66: - Fields reference Kubernetes core v1 types correctly\n67: - JSON tags use camelCase\n68: \n69: ---\n70: \n71: ### [ ] TASK-004: Define AgentRuntimeSpec\n72: **Description**: Create `AgentRuntimeSpec` struct with all required fields and default values.\n73: \n74: **Implementation File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n75: \n76: **Requirements**:\n77: - `MaxSessionDuration string` - default \"8h\"\n78: - `SessionTimeout string` - default \"15m\"\n79: - `TargetPort []TargetPort` - minimum 1 item required\n80: - `PodTemplate PodTemplateSpec` - required field\n81: - Default value markers: `+kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"` and `+kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"`\n82: \n83: **Verification**:\n84: ```bash\n85: go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/ -run TestAgentRuntimeSpec\n86: ```\n87: \n88: **Acceptance Criteria**:\n89: - `AgentRuntimeSpec` struct compiles without errors\n90: - Default value markers are correctly applied\n91: - Required fields are properly tagged\n92: - `TargetPort` has `+kubebuilder:validation:MinItems=1` marker\n93: \n94: ---\n95: \n96: ### [ ] TASK-005: Define AgentRuntimeStatus\n97: **Description**: Create `AgentRuntimeStatus` struct with conditions and observed generation.\n98: \n99: **Implementation File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n100: \n101: **Requirements**:\n102: - `Conditions []metav1.Condition` - optional field\n103: - `ObservedGeneration int64` - optional field\n104: - Follows Kubernetes status conventions\n105: \n106: **Verification**:\n107: ```bash\n108: go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/ -run TestAgentRuntimeStatus\n109: ```\n110: \n111: **Acceptance Criteria**:\n112: - `AgentRuntimeStatus` struct compiles without errors\n113: - `Conditions` field uses standard Kubernetes `metav1.Condition` type\n114: - JSON tags use camelCase with `omitempty` for optional fields\n115: \n116: ---\n117: \n118: ### [ ] TASK-006: Define AgentRuntime main type\n119: **Description**: Create `AgentRuntime` struct with TypeMeta, ObjectMeta, Spec, and Status.\n120: \n121: **Implementation File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n122: \n123: **Requirements**:\n124: - Embeds `metav1.TypeMeta` and `metav1.ObjectMeta`\n125: - Contains `Spec AgentRuntimeSpec` and `Status AgentRuntimeStatus`\n126: - Kubebuilder markers:\n127:   - `+kubebuilder:object:root=true`\n128:   - `+kubebuilder:subresource:status`\n129:   - `+kubebuilder:resource:shortName=art`\n130:   - `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"`\n131: \n132: **Verification**:\n133: ```bash\n134: go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/ -run TestAgentRuntime\n135: ```\n136: \n137: **Acceptance Criteria**:\n138: - `AgentRuntime` struct compiles without errors\n139: - All kubebuilder markers are present and correct\n140: - ShortName \"art\" is configured\n141: - Print column for Age is configured\n142: \n143: ---\n144: \n145: ### [ ] TASK-007: Define AgentRuntimeList type\n146: **Description**: Create `AgentRuntimeList` struct for collection operations.\n147: \n148: *