ce Criteria**:\n258: - Types are registered in scheme\n259: - `runtime.Object` interface is implemented\n260: - `DeepCopy` methods will be generated\n261: \n262: ---\n263: \n264: ## Phase 3: Code Generation\n265: ### [ ] TASK-012: Generate DeepCopy methods\n266: **Description**: Run controller-gen to generate `zz_generated.deepcopy.go`.\n267: \n268: **Command**:\n269: ```bash\n270: controller-gen object paths=\"./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...\"\n271: ```\n272: \n273: **Verification**:\n274: ```bash\n275: test -f pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go && echo \"DeepCopy methods generated\" || echo \"Generation failed\"\n276: ```\n277: \n278: **Acceptance Criteria**:\n279: - `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` file exists\n280: - Contains `DeepCopy()` methods for all types\n281: - Contains `DeepCopyInto()` methods for all types\n282: - Contains `DeepCopyObject()` methods implementing `runtime.Object`\n283: - No compilation errors in generated code\n284: \n285: ---\n286: \n287: ### [ ] TASK-013: Test DeepCopy methods\n288: **Description**: Write and run tests to verify DeepCopy methods work correctly.\n289: \n290: **Test File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types_test.go`\n291: \n292: **Test Cases**:\n293: - Test `DeepCopy()` creates independent copies\n294: - Test modifications to copy don't affect original\n295: - Test nested structs are deep copied\n296: - Test slice fields are deep copied\n297: \n298: **Verification**:\n299: ```bash\n300: go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/ -run TestDeepCopy -v\n301: ```\n302: \n303: **Acceptance Criteria**:\n304: - All DeepCopy tests pass\n305: - Copies are independent from originals\n306: - No shared references between original and copy\n307: \n308: ---\n309: \n310: ### [ ] TASK-014: Generate CRD YAML manifests\n311: **Description**: Run controller-gen to generate CRD YAML files.\n312: \n313: **Command**:\n314: ```bash\n315: controller-gen crd paths=\"./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...\" output:crd:dir=manifests/chart