{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775851450968,"sessionID":"ses_28701c770ffe7IF9hHkfCd4Qlx","part":{"id":"prt_d78feb255001bB7XNdtAYRBtgu","messageID":"msg_d78fea91e00137o7zMJs764nJ3","sessionID":"ses_28701c770ffe7IF9hHkfCd4Qlx","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775851524469,"sessionID":"ses_28701c770ffe7IF9hHkfCd4Qlx","part":{"id":"prt_d78ffd12c001gsxDKsSBUycz2U","messageID":"msg_d78fea91e00137o7zMJs764nJ3","sessionID":"ses_28701c770ffe7IF9hHkfCd4Qlx","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-f758a8b7a89a4ad68a1c7fedd2f28942","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-011 Delta Specification: Router JWT 认证与签发\n\n## Purpose\n\n实现 Router 模块的 JWT（JSON Web Token）认证与签发功能，为 AgentCube 平台提供安全的会话认证机制。该模块负责生成、验证和管理 JWT 令牌，用于认证和授权 Router 请求，确保只有合法的会话才能访问后端服务。\n\n## Requirements\n\n### Requirement: JWT 令牌生成与会话关联\n\nThe system SHALL generate a JWT token for each session using RS256 signing algorithm with the session ID included in the claims.\n\n#### Scenario: 生成包含会话 ID 的 JWT 令牌\n- **GIVEN** a valid session ID and initialized JWT manager with RSA key pair\n- **WHEN** GenerateToken is called with the session ID\n- **THEN** a JWT token is returned with session_id claim containing the provided session ID\n- **AND** the token includes standard RegisteredClaims with IssuedAt, ExpiresAt, and NotBefore timestamps\n- **AND** the token is signed using RS256 algorithm\n\n#### Scenario: 生成的令牌包含标准声明\n- **GIVEN** a JWT manager initialized with private key\n- **WHEN** a token is generated\n- **THEN** the token contains IssuedAt set to current time\n- **AND** ExpiresAt is set to current time plus jwtTokenExpiration (5 minutes)\n- **AND** NotBefore is set to current time\n\n#### Scenario: 生成令牌失败当私钥未初始化\n- **GIVEN** a JWT manager without initialized private key\n- **WHEN** GenerateToken is called\n- **THEN** an error is returned indicating JWT manager not initialized with private key\n\n### Requirement: JWT 令牌验证与签名检查\n\nThe system SHALL validate JWT tokens by verifying the RSA signature and checking expiration time.\n\n#### Scenario: 验证有效的 JWT 令牌\n- **GIVEN** a valid JWT token generated by the system\n- **WHEN** ValidateToken is called with the token string\n- **THEN** the JWT claims are successfully extracted\n- **AND** the session_id claim contains the original session ID\n- **AND** no error is returned\n\n#### Scenario: 验证过期令牌\n- **GIVEN** a JWT token that has expired (ExpiresAt is in the past)\n- **WHEN** ValidateToken is called with the token string\n- **THEN** an error is returned indicating the token has expired\n\n#### Scenario: 验证无效签名的令牌\n- **GIVEN** a JWT token with tampered signature\n- **WHEN** ValidateToken is called with the token string\n- **THEN** an error is returned indicating the token is invalid\n\n#### Scenario: 验证格式错误的令牌\n- **GIVEN** a malformed JWT token string\n- **WHEN** ValidateToken is called with the token string\n- **THEN** an error is returned indicating the token format is invalid\n\n#### Scenario: 验证令牌失败当公钥未初始化\n- **GIVEN** a JWT manager without initialized public key\n- **WHEN** ValidateToken is called\n- **THEN** an error is returned indicating JWT manager not initialized with public key\n\n### Requirement: RSA 密钥对生成\n\nThe system SHALL generate RSA 2048-bit key pairs for JWT signing and verification.\n\n#### Scenario: 生成 RSA 密钥对\n- **GIVEN** no existing RSA keys\n- **WHEN** generateRSAKeyPair is called\n- **THEN** an RSA private key with 2048 bits is returned\n- **AND** the corresponding public key is derived from the private key\n- **AND** no error is returned\n\n#### Scenario: 密钥对包含私钥和公钥\n- **GIVEN** a generated RSA key pair\n- **WHEN** the key pair is examined\n- **THEN** the private key can be used for signing\n- **AND** the public key can be used for verification\n- **AND** the public key matches the private key\n\n### Requirement: 密钥持久化到 Kubernetes Secret\n\nThe system SHALL store RSA keys in a Kubernetes Secret named \"agentcube-jwt-keys\" with private.pem and public.pem data fields.\n\n#### Scenario: 首次启动时创建密钥 Secret\n- **GIVEN** a Kubernetes cluster and no existing JWT key Secret\n- **WHEN** NewJWTManager is called with a valid clientset and namespace\n- **THEN** a new Secret is created with name \"agentcube-jwt-keys\"\n- **AND** the Secret contains \"private.pem\" with PEM-encoded private key\n- **AND** the Secret contains \"public.pem\" with PEM-encoded public key\n- **AND** the Secret is created in the specified namespace\n\n#### Scenario: 从现有 Secret 加载密钥\n- **GIVEN** a Kubernetes cluster with an existing JWT key Secret\n- **WHEN** NewJWTManager is called\n- **THEN** the existing keys are loaded from the Secret\n- **AND** no new Secret is created\n- **AND** the keys match the values stored in the Secret\n\n#### Scenario: Secret 不存在时生成密钥并存储\n- **GIVEN** a Kubernetes cluster without the JWT key Secret\n- **WHEN** NewJWTManager is called\n- **THEN** new RSA keys are generated\n- **AND** the keys are stored in a new Secret\n- **AND** the JWT manager is initialized with the generated keys\n\n### Requirement: 密钥加载和解析\n\nThe system SHALL parse PEM-encoded RSA keys from Kubernetes Secret data.\n\n#### Scenario: 解析 PEM 编码的私钥\n- **GIVEN** a valid PEM-encoded RSA private key block with type \"RSA PRIVATE KEY\"\n- **WHEN** parsePrivateKeyPEM is called with the PEM data\n- **THEN** an RSA private key is successfully parsed\n- **AND** no error is returned\n\n#### Scenario: 解析 PEM 编码的公钥\n- **GIVEN** a valid PEM-encoded RSA public key block with type \"PUBLIC KEY\"\n- **WHEN** parsePublicKeyPEM is called with the PEM data\n- **THEN** an RSA public key is successfully parsed\n- **AND** no error is returned\n\n#### Scenario: 解析无效的私钥格式\n- **GIVEN** an invalid PEM-encoded private key\n- **WHEN** parsePrivateKeyPEM is called\n- **THEN** an error is returned indicating the PEM block is invalid\n\n#### Scenario: 解析无效的公钥格式\n- **GIVEN** an invalid PEM-encoded public key\n- **WHEN** parsePublicKeyPEM is called\n- **THEN** an error is returned indicating the PEM block is invalid\n\n#### Scenario: Secret 缺少必需的密钥字段\n- **GIVEN** a Secret without \"private.pem\" or \"public.pem\" field\n- **WHEN** loadKeysFromSecret is called with the Secret\n- **THEN** an error is returned indicating the missing field\n\n### Requirement: JWT 管理器初始化\n\nThe system SHALL initialize JWT manager with kubernetes clientset and optionally use default namespace when not specified.\n\n#### Scenario: 使用显式命名空间初始化\n- **GIVEN** a valid kubernetes clientset and a namespace string\n- **WHEN** NewJWTManager is called with the clientset and namespace\n- **THEN** a JWT manager is returned with the configured namespace\n- **AND** the manager is initialized with keys from the Secret or newly generated\n\n#### Scenario: 使用默认命名空间初始化\n- **GIVEN** a valid kubernetes clientset and empty namespace string\n- **WHEN** NewJWTManager is called with empty namespace\n- **THEN** a JWT manager is returned with default namespace (\"agentcube\")\n- **AND** the manager is initialized properly\n\n#### Scenario: 初始化失败当 clientset 为 nil\n- **GIVEN** a nil kubernetes clientset\n- **WHEN** NewJWTManager is called with nil clientset\n- **THEN** an error is returned indicating kubernetes clientset is required\n\n#### Scenario: Secret 访问失败时降级到内存密钥\n- **GIVEN** a kubernetes clientset and permission denied error accessing Secret\n- **WHEN** NewJWTManager is called\n- **THEN** a warning is logged about the failure\n- **AND** RSA keys are generated in memory\n- **AND** the JWT manager is initialized with in-memory keys\n\n### Requirement: JWT 认证中间件\n\nThe system SHALL provide a Gin middleware that validates JWT tokens from Authorization header.\n\n#### Scenario: 中间件验证有效的令牌\n- **GIVEN** a valid JWT token in Authorization header as \"Bearer <token>\"\n- **WHEN** a protected endpoint is called with the middleware applied\n- **THEN** the request proceeds to the handler\n- **AND** the session_id claim is available in the context\n\n#### Scenario: 中间件拒绝缺少令牌的请求\n- **GIVEN** a request without Authorization header\n- **WHEN** a protected endpoint is called\n- **THEN** the request is rejected with 401 Unauthorized\n- **AND** an error response indicates missing token\n\n#### Scenario: 中间件拒绝无效的令牌\n- **GIVEN** a request with invalid JWT token in Authorization header\n- **WHEN** a protected endpoint is called\n- **THEN** the request is rejected with 401 Unauthorized\n- **AND** an error response indicates invalid token\n\n#### Scenario: 中间件拒绝过期令牌\n- **GIVEN** a request with expired JWT token\n- **WHEN** a protected endpoint is called\n- **THEN** the request is rejected with 401 Unauthorized\n- **AND** an error response indicates token expired\n\n### Requirement: 令牌传输格式\n\nThe system SHALL use standard Authorization header with Bearer scheme for token transmission.\n\n#### Scenario: 客户端使用 Bearer scheme 发送令牌\n- **GIVEN** a valid JWT token\n- **WHEN** a client sends a request to protected endpoint\n- **THEN** the Authorization header is set to \"Bearer <token>\"\n\n#### Scenario: 中间件从 Authorization 头提取令牌\n- **GIVEN** a request with Authorization header \"Bearer eyJhbGci...\"\n- **WHEN** the middleware processes the request\n- **THEN** the token \"eyJhbGci...\" is extracted from the header\n\n#### Scenario: 中间件处理非 Bearer scheme\n- **GIVEN** a request with Authorization header using invalid scheme\n- **WHEN** the middleware processes the request\n- **THEN** the request is rejected with 401 Unauthorized\n\n### Requirement: 会话创建时返回令牌\n\nThe system SHALL generate and return a JWT token when a new session is created.\n\n#### Scenario: 创建会话返回 JWT 令牌\n- **GIVEN** a request to create a new session\n- **WHEN** the session is successfully created\n- **THEN** a JWT token is generated for the session\n- **AND** the token is included in the response\n- **AND** the session_id in the token matches the created session\n\n#### Scenario: 响应包含令牌和会话信息\n- **GIVEN** a successfully created session\n- **WHEN** the response is serialized\n- **THEN** the response contains sessionId, sandboxId, sandboxName, and token fields\n- **AND** the token is a valid JWT that can be verified\n\n### Requirement: 错误处理和日志记录\n\nThe system SHALL log key events and provide structured error responses without exposing sensitive information.\n\n#### Scenario: 记录密钥生成事件\n- **GIVEN** a new RSA key pair is generated\n- **WHEN** the keys are stored in Secret\n- **THEN** a log entry indicates successful Secret creation\n- **AND** the log does not expose the private key\n\n#### Scenario: 记录密钥加载事件\n- **GIVEN** existing keys are loaded from Secret\n- **WHEN** loadKeysFromSecret succeeds\n- **THEN** a log entry indicates successful key loading\n- **AND** the log includes the Secret name\n\n#### Scenario: 记录认证失败事件\n- **GIVEN** a request with invalid JWT token\n- **WHEN** the middleware rejects the request\n- **THEN** a warning log entry is created\n- **AND** the log includes the correlation ID\n- **AND** the log does not include the full token\n\n#### Scenario: 返回结构化错误响应\n- **GIVEN** a JWT validation error occurs\n- **WHEN** an error response is generated\n- **THEN** the response includes error message and error code\n- **AND** the message does not expose internal details\n\n### Requirement: 令牌过期时间配置\n\nThe system SHALL use a configurable token expiration time with default of 5 minutes.\n\n#### Scenario: 默认令牌过期时间为 5 分钟\n- **GIVEN** a token is generated with default configuration\n- **WHEN** the token is examined\n- **THEN** the ExpiresAt claim is set to IssuedAt plus 5 minutes\n\n#### Scenario: 配置的过期时间生效\n- **GIVEN** a custom token expiration time is configured\n- **WHEN** a token is generated\n- **THEN** the ExpiresAt claim is set to IssuedAt plus the configured time\n\n### Requirement: 密钥加密和 PEM 编码\n\nThe system SHALL encode RSA keys in PEM format with correct block types.\n\n#### Scenario: 私钥使用 PKCS1 编码\n- **GIVEN** an RSA private key\n- **WHEN** encodeToPEM is called\n- **THEN** the PEM block has type \"RSA PRIVATE KEY\"\n- **AND** the key is encoded using PKCS1 format\n\n#### Scenario: 公钥使用 PKIX 编码\n- **GIVEN** an RSA public key\n- **WHEN** encodeToPEM is called\n- **THEN** the PEM block has type \"PUBLIC KEY\"\n- **AND** the key is encoded using PKIX format\n\n#### Scenario: 解码时验证 PEM 类型\n- **GIVEN** a PEM-encoded block\n- **WHEN** parsePrivateKeyPEM is called\n- **THEN** the function verifies the block type is \"RSA PRIVATE KEY\"\n- **AND** rejects blocks with incorrect type\n\n#### Scenario: 解码时验证公钥类型\n- **GIVEN** a PEM-encoded block\n- **WHEN** parsePublicKeyPEM is called\n- **THEN** the function verifies the block type is \"PUBLIC KEY\"\n- **AND** rejects blocks with incorrect type\n\n### Requirement: Secret 访问权限验证\n\nThe system SHALL handle Secret access errors gracefully and provide clear error messages.\n\n#### Scenario: Secret 不存在时创建新 Secret\n- **GIVEN** a request for Secret that returns 404 Not Found\n- **WHEN** tryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret is called\n- **THEN** a new Secret is created with generated keys\n- **AND** no error is returned\n\n#### Scenario: Secret 权限被拒绝时降级\n- **GIVEN** a request for Secret that returns 403 Forbidden\n- **WHEN** tryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret is called\n- **THEN** an error is logged\n- **AND** in-memory keys are generated as fallback\n\n#### Scenario: Secret API 错误时处理\n- **GIVEN** a Kubernetes API error accessing Secret\n- **WHEN** Secret operations are performed\n- **THEN** the error is wrapped with context\n- **AND** a clear error message is returned\n\n### Requirement: JWT 声明结构\n\nThe system SHALL use standard JWT claims with custom session_id field.\n\n#### Scenario: 声明包含会话 ID\n- **GIVEN** a JWTClaims struct\n- **WHEN** the struct is populated with session ID\n- **THEN** the SessionID field is set to the provided value\n- **AND** the field is JSON-encoded as \"session_id\"\n\n#### Scenario: 声明包含标准 RegisteredClaims\n- **GIVEN** a JWTClaims struct\n- **WHEN** the struct is used for token generation\n- **THEN** the token includes standard claims: Issuer, Subject, Audience, ExpiresAt, IssuedAt, NotBefore, ID\n\n#### Scenario: 声明支持 JSON 序列化\n- **GIVEN** a JWTClaims struct with populated fields\n- **WHEN** the struct is serialized to JSON\n- **THEN** all fields are correctly encoded in camelCase\n- **AND** the JSON is valid and can be deserialized\n\n### Requirement: 并发安全\n\nThe system SHALL support concurrent token generation and validation operations.\n\n#### Scenario: 并发生成多个令牌\n- **GIVEN** multiple goroutines calling GenerateToken simultaneously\n- **WHEN** the tokens are generated\n- **THEN** all tokens are successfully generated\n- **AND** each token has a unique session_id\n- **AND** no race conditions occur\n\n#### Scenario: 并发验证多个令牌\n- **GIVEN** multiple goroutines calling ValidateToken simultaneously\n- **WHEN** the tokens are validated\n- **THEN** all validations are performed correctly\n- **AND** no race conditions occur\n\n### Requirement: 令牌签名算法验证\n\nThe system SHALL verify the signing algorithm used in tokens to prevent algorithm confusion attacks.\n\n#### Scenario: 拒绝非 RSA 签名算法\n- **GIVEN** a JWT token signed with HS256 (HMAC) algorithm\n- **WHEN** ValidateToken is called\n- **THEN** an error is returned indicating unexpected signing method\n\n#### Scenario: 验证 RS256 签名算法\n- **GIVEN** a JWT token signed with RS256 algorithm\n- **WHEN** ValidateToken is called\n- **THEN** the signature is verified using RSA public key\n- **AND** the token is accepted if valid\n\n#### Scenario: 检测算法头篡改\n- **GIVEN** a JWT token with \"alg\" header modified to \"none\"\n- **WHEN** ValidateToken is called\n- **THEN** an error is returned indicating unexpected signing method\n\n### Requirement: 令牌过期验证\n\nThe system SHALL reject tokens that have passed their expiration time.\n\n#### Scenario: 拒绝刚刚过期的令牌\n- **GIVEN** a token that expired 1 second ago\n- **WHEN** ValidateToken is called\n- **THEN** an error is returned indicating the token has expired\n\n#### Scenario: 接受未过期的令牌\n- **GIVEN** a token that expires in the future\n- **WHEN** ValidateToken is called\n- **THEN** the token is validated successfully\n- **AND** the claims are returned\n\n#### Scenario: NotBefore 验证\n- **GIVEN** a token with NotBefore set to future time\n- **WHEN** ValidateToken is called before NotBefore time\n- **THEN** an error is returned indicating the token is not yet valid\n\n### Requirement: 命名空间隔离\n\nThe system SHALL use the configured namespace for Secret operations.\n\n#### Scenario: 使用指定命名空间访问 Secret\n- **GIVEN** a JWT manager configured with namespace \"production\"\n- **WHEN** Secret operations are performed\n- **THEN** the Secret is accessed in the \"production\" namespace\n- **AND** operations do not affect other namespaces\n\n#### Scenario: 使用默认命名空间\n- **GIVEN** a JWT manager initialized without namespace\n- **WHEN** Secret operations are performed\n- **THEN** the default namespace (\"agentcube\") is used\n- **AND** Secret is accessed in the default namespace\n\n### Requirement: Secret 命名约定\n\nThe system SHALL use a consistent Secret name for key storage.\n\n#### Scenario: Secret 名称固定为 \"agentcube-jwt-keys\"\n- **GIVEN** any JWT manager instance\n- **WHEN** Secret operations are performed\n- **THEN** the Secret name is always \"agentcube-jwt-keys\"\n- **AND** the Secret is stored and retrieved using this name\n\n### Requirement: JWT 管理器不可变密钥\n\nThe system SHALL not allow key regeneration after initialization.\n\n#### Scenario: 初始化后密钥保持不变\n- **GIVEN** a JWT manager initialized with keys\n- **WHEN** multiple calls to GenerateToken are made\n- **THEN** all tokens are signed with the same private key\n- **AND** all tokens can be verified with the same public key\n\n#### Scenario: 重启后密钥从 Secret 加载\n- **GIVEN** a JWT manager that stored keys in Secret\n- **WHEN** the service is restarted and JWT manager is reinitialized\n- **THEN** the same keys are loaded from the Secret\n- **AND** previously issued tokens remain valid\n\n### Requirement: 性能要求\n\nThe system SHALL meet performance targets for token operations.\n\n#### Scenario: 令牌生成延迟\n- **GIVEN** a JWT manager initialized with keys\n- **WHEN** GenerateToken is called multiple times\n- **THEN** the P99 latency is less than 10ms\n\n#### Scenario: 令牌验证延迟\n- **GIVEN** a valid JWT token\n- **WHEN** ValidateToken is called multiple times\n- **THEN** the P99 latency is less than 5ms\n\n### Requirement: 日志级别控制\n\nThe system SHALL use appropriate log levels for different events.\n\n#### Scenario: 信息日志用于正常操作\n- **GIVEN** successful key loading or Secret creation\n- **WHEN** these operations complete\n- **THEN** log entries use Info level\n- **AND** include relevant context\n\n#### Scenario: 警告日志用于降级场景\n- **GIVEN** Secret access failure with fallback to in-memory keys\n- **WHEN** the fallback occurs\n- **THEN** log entries use Warning level\n- **AND** include the original error\n\n#### Scenario: 错误日志用于失败场景\n- **GIVEN** critical failures like key generation errors\n- **WHEN** these failures occur\n- **THEN** log entries use Error level\n- **AND** include detailed error information\n\n### Requirement: 上下文传递\n\nThe system SHALL pass session information to request handlers after successful authentication.\n\n#### Scenario: 中间件设置会话 ID 到上下文\n- **GIVEN** a valid JWT token with session_id claim\n- **WHEN** the middleware successfully validates the token\n- **THEN** the session_id is stored in the Gin context\n- **AND** handlers can retrieve it from the context\n\n#### Scenario: 处理器从上下文获取会话 ID\n- **GIVEN** a request authenticated with JWT token\n- **WHEN** a handler needs the session ID\n- **THEN** the handler retrieves it from the Gin context\n- **AND** uses it for session-specific operations","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-011/delta-spec.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/workloadmanager/gc/collector_test.go\">\nERROR [127:15] expected 1 expression\n</diagnostics>\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/workloadmanager/controller/reconciler/codeinterpreter.go\">\nERROR [63:7] undefined: statusConditionsEqual\nERROR [106:6] undefined: statusConditionsEqual\nERROR [173:2] declared and not used: logger\nERROR [242:5] undefined: podSpecsEqual\nERROR [267:29] undefined: convertEnvVars\nERROR [274:25] undefined: convertResources\nERROR [326:6] undefined: statusConditionsEqual\n</diagnostics>\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/workloadmanager/controller/reconciler/controller.go\">\nERROR [57:3] unknown field MetricsBindAddress in struct literal of type controllerruntime.Options\nERROR [58:3] unknown field Port in struct literal of type controllerruntime.Options\nERROR [62:3] unknown field SyncPeriod in struct literal of type controllerruntime.Options\nERROR [88:17] undefined: AgentRuntimeReconciler\nERROR [98:15] cannot use ctrl.Options{…} (value of struct type controllerruntime.Options) as controller.TypedOptions[reconcile.Request] value in argument to ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).For(&runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime{}).WithEventFilter(&ResourceGenerationChangedPredicate{}).WithOptions\nERROR [98:28] unknown field MaxConcurrentReconciles in struct literal of type controllerruntime.Options\nERROR [118:15] cannot use ctrl.Options{…} (value of struct type controllerruntime.Options) as controller.TypedOptions[reconcile.Request] value in argument to ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).For(&runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter{}).WithEventFilter(&ResourceGenerationChangedPredicate{}).WithOptions\nERROR [118:28] unknown field MaxConcurrentReconciles in struct literal of type controllerruntime.Options\n</diagnostics>","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/router/jwt.go":[{"range":{"start":{"line":86,"character":86},"end":{"line":86,"character":97}},"severity":4,"code":"default","codeDescription":{"href":"https://pkg.go.dev/golang.org/x/tools/go/ana